data.description: Such a cute, clean, updated home ready to host all your new memories! Brand new carpet, freshly painted neutral interior, new appliances including dishwasher, refrigerator, oven/range, microwave and disposal. From the welcoming front porch to the fully fenced back yard, you will find so much to love about this home. Open floor plan including great room with cathedral ceiling, accent lighting and cozy gas log fireplace. Prepare meals in the bright updated kitchen offering a breakfast bar, breakfast nook, atrium door to the back yard and large pantry. The more formal dining room can be the backdrop for dinners during those special occasions. Split bedroom floor plan provides privacy in the primary bedroom suite complete w/double sink vanity and walk in closet. Two well sized bedrooms and full bath anchor the opposite end of the home. Whether cooking inside or grilling outside, you will find abundant entertaining space for your family and guests. 2 car garage with attic access and pull-down stairs. Storage barn in the back yard. Great location in Lawrence with easy access to Binford Blvd, an easy drive to downtown, I-69 and 465. Just around the corner from Restaurants and shops.  Come make this home.
